Using LinkedIn and completing my profile has helped me better understand how I want to present myself professionally and what kind of opportunities I am aiming for. 
While filling out sections like the headline, summary, and skills, I had to think carefully about my strengths, experiences, and future goals instead of just listing 
basic information. Adding details such as a profile photo, education, projects, and relevant skills also made me realize how important a complete and well-structured 
profile is for making a strong first impression on recruiters and potential connections.
